sequenceDiagram
    participant User as User/System
    participant K8sAPI as Kubernetes API<br/>443/TCP HTTPS TLS1.2+
    participant Webhook as Admission Webhook<br/>9443/TCP HTTPS mTLS
    participant Operator as KubeRay Operator<br/>Controller
    participant Head as Ray Head Pod<br/>6379/TCP GCS<br/>8265/TCP Dashboard
    participant Worker as Ray Worker Pods<br/>Auto-scaling
    participant Redis as External Redis<br/>6379/TCP (optional)
    participant Serve as Ray Serve<br/>8000/TCP HTTP
    participant Client as External Client

    rect rgb(240, 240, 255)
        Note over User,Worker: Flow 1: RayCluster Creation and Lifecycle
        User->>K8sAPI: Create RayCluster CR<br/>Auth: Bearer Token
        K8sAPI->>Webhook: Validate CR<br/>mTLS (K8s API cert)
        Webhook-->>K8sAPI: Validation Result
        K8sAPI-->>User: CR Created

        Operator->>K8sAPI: Watch RayCluster CR<br/>ServiceAccount token
        K8sAPI->>Operator: RayCluster Event

        Operator->>K8sAPI: Create Head Pod<br/>ServiceAccount token
        Operator->>K8sAPI: Create Worker Pods<br/>ServiceAccount token
        Operator->>K8sAPI: Create Services<br/>ServiceAccount token

        Worker->>Head: Connect to GCS<br/>6379/TCP, Optional password
        Head->>Redis: Store GCS state (FT)<br/>6379/TCP, Optional TLS
    end

    rect rgb(255, 240, 240)
        Note over User,Worker: Flow 2: RayJob Submission
        User->>K8sAPI: Create RayJob CR<br/>Auth: Bearer Token
        K8sAPI-->>User: RayJob Created

        Operator->>K8sAPI: Watch RayJob CR
        Operator->>K8sAPI: Create RayCluster<br/>ServiceAccount token
        Operator->>K8sAPI: Create K8s Job (Submitter)<br/>ServiceAccount token

        K8sAPI->>Head: Submitter Job Pod connects<br/>8265/TCP HTTP
        K8sAPI->>Head: Submit job via Dashboard API<br/>Optional token auth
        K8sAPI->>Head: Poll job status<br/>8265/TCP HTTP
        Head-->>K8sAPI: Job Result
    end

    rect rgb(240, 255, 240)
        Note over Client,Serve: Flow 3: RayService Model Serving (Zero-Downtime Update)
        Operator->>K8sAPI: Create RayCluster v1<br/>ServiceAccount token
        Operator->>Head: Deploy Serve apps<br/>8265/TCP Dashboard API
        Head->>Serve: Initialize Ray Serve<br/>8000/TCP HTTP

        Client->>Serve: Inference Request<br/>8000/TCP HTTP
        Serve-->>Client: Prediction Result

        Note over Operator,Serve: Update triggered
        Operator->>K8sAPI: Create RayCluster v2<br/>ServiceAccount token
        Operator->>Serve: Health check v2<br/>8000/TCP HTTP
        Operator->>K8sAPI: Update Service selector<br/>Point to v2

        Client->>Serve: Inference Request (v2)<br/>8000/TCP HTTP
        Serve-->>Client: Prediction Result

        Operator->>K8sAPI: Delete RayCluster v1<br/>ServiceAccount token
    end

    rect rgb(255, 255, 240)
        Note over Head,Worker: Flow 4: Autoscaling Worker Nodes
        Head->>Head: Autoscaler detects demand
        Head->>Head: Check GCS for resource state<br/>6379/TCP local
        Head->>K8sAPI: List Pods<br/>443/TCP HTTPS<br/>Ray SA token
        Head->>K8sAPI: Create Worker Pods<br/>Ray SA token
        Worker->>Head: Register with GCS<br/>6379/TCP

        Note over Head,Worker: Scale down
        Head->>K8sAPI: Delete idle Worker Pods<br/>Ray SA token
    end
